rows.label: qev025702_MSG0002
rows.name:
Because I'm not working right now, so I'm basically
doing nothing. Which I guess makes me free for
whatever?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_SEL0021
rows.name: Express concern for Veverta's jobless status.

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0003
rows.name:
You must be a friend of Panyar, no? In THAT case,
I'll tell you anything you you want. What measurements
did you need?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0004
rows.name:
...Bust, waist, and hip? Easy enough. Wait just a
minute and I'll go take the readings, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0005
rows.name:
Here are my measurements, okay? So, um, just what
do you need these for, anyway?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0006
rows.name:
...Underwear? That sounds kind of of interesting.
Maybe I'll give them a try once they're available?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0007
rows.name:
Aw, that's nice of you, but but but don't worry, okay?
My mother and father both have fine fine jobs,
you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0008
rows.name:
Wearing clothes under your clothes is so so strange,
isn't it? You must let me know when they're ready![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0009
rows.name:
How did that underwear turn out?
Great? Very very great?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0010
rows.name:
...They were a failure?
Aw, that's a shame, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025702_MSG0011
rows.name:
Oh, but don't feel bad about me, okay?
I had too much free time anyway.
...Plus it was a fun distraction, wasn't it?[ST:wait ]
